sources.description:
Luster - A troubled businessman trying to make sense of a life out-of-control, discovers that the man working against him is another side of his own personality. As he fights back against his manipulative alter-ego, murder madness and mayhem ensue.
2010.  Stars: Andrew Howard, Tess Panzer, Matthew Rhys
